<tr>
<td>
<p><b><a href="/wiki/Sami_languages" title="Sami languages">Sami languages</a></b>:<br />
<a href="/wiki/Northern_Sami" title="Northern Sami">Northern Sami</a>, <a href="/wiki/Lule_Sami" title="Lule Sami">Lule Sami</a>, <a href="/wiki/Pite_Sami" title="Pite Sami">Pite Sami</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ume_Sami" title="Ume Sami">Ume Sami</a>, <a href="/wiki/Southern_Sami" title="Southern Sami">Southern Sami</a>, <a href="/wiki/Inari_Sami" title="Inari Sami">Inari Sami</a>, <a href="/wiki/Skolt_Sami" title="Skolt Sami">Skolt Sami</a>, <a href="/wiki/Kildin_Sami" title="Kildin Sami">Kildin Sami</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ter_Sami" title="Ter Sami">Ter Sami</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Akkala_Sami" title="Akkala Sami">Akkala Sami</a> (extinct), <a href="/wiki/Kemi_Sami" title="Kemi Sami">Kemi Sami</a> (extinct)</p>
<b>Nation State Languages</b>:<br />
<a href="/wiki/Norwegian_language" title="Norwegian language">Norwegian</a>, <a href="/wiki/Swedish_language" title="Swedish language">Swedish</a>, <a href="/wiki/Finnish_language" title="Finnish language">Finnish</a>, <a href="/wiki/Russian_language" title="Russian language">Russian</a></td>
