<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sami_people&amp;action=edit&amp;section=50" title="Edit section: Sami Government and Policy">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Sami Government and Policy</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Dislocation_of_Sami_people" title="Dislocation of Sami people">Dislocation of Sami people</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Norwegianization" title="Norwegianization">Norwegianization</a> Government program to forcibly assimilate the Sami into Norwegian culture.</li>
